title: Jewel Live At Humprey's By The Bay 2004
description: Shot over two performances on a summer night just before the launch of her "This Way Tour". Live At Humprey's By The Bay is Jewel's first ever concert DVD. This DVD captures the true essence of this mult-platinum singer/songwriter's decade long career. Some of the songs include Hands,Everything Breaks Sometimes,You Were Meant For Me. This concert brings you a front row seat in an intimate setting
